### Objective

Build the core workspace experience of BEFRIX.

The platform does not execute automations.

All business logic, calculations, AI processing and workflow execution are performed externally by N8N and persisted in Supabase.

The frontend only consumes and visualizes data.

---

# Dashboard Structure

Create:

/dashboard

Sidebar:

* Dashboard
* Leads
* Campaigns
* Analytics
* AI Insights
* Workflows
* Events
* Messages
* Meetings
* Billing
* Settings

Conditional:

* Admin

Visible only when user role allows.

